Class DataResponse

  • java.lang.Object
    • neustar.registry.jtoolkit2.se.ReceiveSE
      • neustar.registry.jtoolkit2.se.Response
        • neustar.registry.jtoolkit2.se.DataResponse
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    CheckResponse, CreateResponse, DomainRenewResponse, DomainVariantInfoResponse, FundInfoResponse, InfoResponse, NotificationResponse, TransferResponse

    public abstract class DataResponse
extends Response
    The base class of all response classes which provide more information than the standard Response class. Such classes model EPP responses having a resData element. Subclasses must specify the command and object types to which the response applies.
